{"tid":2251148,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特首：多用收回土地條例　劉業強料政府欠能量應付磨擦","createTime":"2020-10-20T14:52:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T15:26:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"84cd713c0ef366206709113d3f70e83163f95e4d","tid":2251148,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T14:52:00.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥表示，日後將會更多運用《收回土地條例》，收回近400公頃私人土地。鄉議局主席劉業強出席鄉議局會議後，被問到會否影響原居民權益，他說相信政府經過連串社會事件，欠缺能量應付更多社會的磨擦，期望政府可以平衡發展與和諧，雙方多溝通，又指新界人會配合政府發展。<br />\n<br />\n劉業強表示，政府預留予鄉村發展的土地約900公頃，每年申請及獲批的申請少，對鄉村高空發展持開放態度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555797-20201020.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555797-20201020.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QSBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=f7d8a415\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555797-20201020.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2c3faf2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555797-20201020.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"062322aa461d24b18eeeebac96a83e802cfd42e7","tid":2251148,"uid":2692,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T14:57:29.000Z","msg":"飛鳥盡，良弓藏<br />\n狡兔死，走狗烹"},{"pid":"02acefc15d72820a8bbf55d8d61354b8126178ea","tid":2251148,"uid":95577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T15:05:21.000Z","msg":"算鳩數啦<br />\n當然又話要郁鄉村<br />\n俾人燒林門鄭氏<br />\n過左咁多年<br />\n郁過啲乜？"},{"pid":"71158944766f5365f76a72b4d7db8a549fea760e","tid":2251148,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T15:07:36.000Z","msg":"叫隊防暴隊衝入去咪得<br />\n咩野應付唔到磨擦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4a0b7ad53b33abd3ba18b916bec4fac80e95f1","ti